          <title>
            <string language="en">Independence National Historic Park</string>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Unabhängigkeit-Nationaler Historischer Park</string>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Parc Historique National de l'Indépendance</string>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Parque Historic Nacional Da Independência</string>
            <string language="x-mt-it">Parco Storico Nazionale Di Indipendenza</string>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Εθνικό ιστορικό πάρκο ανεξαρτησίας</string>
            <string language="x-mt-es">Parque Histórico Nacional De la Independencia</string>
          </title>
          <description>
            <string language="en">presents portraits and descriptions of Nathanael Greene, Alexander Hamilton, John Paul Jones, George Washington, and more than two dozen other battlefield heroes of the American Revolution.</string>
          </description>
          <keyword>
            <string language="en">Social Sciences</string>
          </keyword>
          <language>en</language>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Geschenkportraits und Beschreibungen von Nathanael
Greene, von Alexander Hamilton, von John Paul Jones, von George 
Washington und von mehr als zwei Dutzend anderen Schlachtfeld Heldern 
der amerikanischen Umdrehung.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">verticales de présents et descriptions de 
Nathanael Greene, d'Alexandre Hamilton, de John Paul Jones, de 
George Washington, et de plus de deux héros de douzaine autres 
champs de bataille de la révolution américaine.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">retratos dos presentes e descrições de Nathanael
Greene, de Alexander Hamilton, de John Paul Jones, de George 
Washington, e de mais de outros dois heróis de dúzia campos de 
batalha da volta americana.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-it">ritratti dei presenti e descrizioni di 
Nathanael Greene, di Alexander Hamilton, di John Paul Jones, di George
Washington e di più di altri due eroi dei dozzina campi di 
battaglia della rivoluzione americana.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-el">παρουσιάζει τα πορτρέτα και τις περιγραφές Nathanael
Greene, του Αλεξάνδρου Χάμιλτον, John Paul Jones, 
George Ουάσιγκτον, και περισσότερων από δύο δωδεκάων άλλων 
ηρώων πεδίων μαχών της αμερικανικής επανάστασης.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-es">retratos de los presentes y descripciones de 
Nathanael Greene, de Alexander Hamilton, de Juan Paul Jones, de George
Washington, y de más de dos héroes de docena otros campos de batalla
de la revolución americana.</string>
          </description>
          <keyword>
